text: Md. Shamsul Haque is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-2. He was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-11 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1991 and 1996. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
